    <LessonDescription/>
    <opTopTitle>Course Overview</opTopTitle>
    <opTopContent>&lt;p&gt;This lesson is for teachers who are interested in implementing digital game-based learning in their classroom. The purpose of this lesson is to design a learning activity that uses digital game-based strategies to deepen student engagement and learning in the classroom.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Lesson Objectives:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;1. Evaluate the usage of digital game-based learning practices in a classroom.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;2. Create a digital game-based activity for your educational environment.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;3. Create a lesson plan for implementing any digital game-based learning approach for your classroom.&lt;/p&gt;</opTopContent>
